      <license>PHP License</license>
      <state>stable</state>
      <notes>ps_hyphenate() did not return an array but true. Added more tests
       and examples. Many internal changes.
</notes>
    </release>
    <release>
      <version>1.2.0</version>
      <date>2004-04-26</date>
      <license>PHP License</license>
      <state>stable</state>
      <notes>Added new function ps_string_geometry(), ps_set_text_pos(),
 ps_symbol(), ps_symbol_name(), ps_symbol_width(), ps_begin_pattern(),
